         <abstract>
            <p>A California water utility's desire to move away from the dangers of gas chlorination drove operators and managers to consider bulk hypochlorite delivery and on-site hypochlorite generation as disinfection options. Ultimately, they found an on-site hypochlorite generation system was manageable, got the job done, and made the utility a better neighbor.</p>
